txt.en: Birdhouses can be found at Rhosgobel in Laerlad.\n\nYou should repair birdhouses for Radagast.

'With my absence from Rhosgobel and all that has transpired here, it would seem many of my birdhouses lie in disrepair. If you have a moment, would you tend to the homes of my friends? I am sure they would be most grateful!'
The birdhouses of Rhosgobel are in need of repair.
Radagast can be found at Rhosgobel.\n\nYou should talk to Radagast.
'You have done as I asked? I am glad to hear, and my bird friends are glad as well! They shall roost in comfort!'
